    section#sample-buttons
      .container
        h3 Buttons
        
        p.
          Buttons are a really basic elements on any web page or app, and it 
          comes in two different flavors in Seeds. The standard is plain and 
          the colored has a vibrant primary color. In order to use the primary 
          just add the class name <code >.btn-primary</code>. If you need use 
          anchor (&lt;a /&gt;) as button, include the <code >.btn</code> class 
          name on it.
        
